一些看法認為，[[邪教|邪教]]與正當宗教之間，有真正的區別，而邪教與正當宗教之間的其中一個區別在於洗腦，精神控制的研究認為，強制勸說常常通过若干關鍵步骤完成：<ref>Galanter, 1989; Mithers, 1994; Ofshe & Watters, 1994; Singer, Temerlin, & Langone, 1990; Zimbardo & leipper, 1991</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Uy1gmwcAgg4C&pg=PA46&lpg=PA46&dq=coercive+persuasion,+psychology&source=bl&ots=XAdQttkc02&sig=SPrlMB_4ggub6N49xR6RTgHk3wI&hl=en&ei=zB0YStrjFsyYtgf0tJDsDA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=6#PPA46,M1 |title=Cordón, ''Popular Psychology'' 46–47 |accessdate=2011-01-01 |archive-date=2014-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141001154332/http://books.google.com/books?id=Uy1gmwcAgg4C&pg=PA46&lpg=PA46&dq=coercive+persuasion,+psychology&source=bl&ots=XAdQttkc02&sig=SPrlMB_4ggub6N49xR6RTgHk3wI&hl=en&ei=zB0YStrjFsyYtgf0tJDsDA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=6#PPA46,M1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*参入者的身體或情緒被处于一种不安的状况；
*他們的所有問題被歸結為一個簡單的解釋，并且这个解釋被反复強調；
*他們常常得到一個有魅力的領導人或群体的無條件的愛和接納；
*他們在组织内得到了一個新的身份；
*他們被与朋友、親戚和[[主流|主流]]文化隔離开，接触外部资讯受到嚴格控制。<ref>Psychology 101, Carole Wade et al., 2005</ref>

然而，并不是所有的研究者都同意这种观点。<ref name="Gene G. James">Gene G. James, ''Brainwashing: The Myth and the Actuality''  Fordham University Quarterly, Volume LXI, June 1986</ref><ref>Novit Evas, Bette ''Interpreting the Free Exercise of Religion: The Constitution and American Pluralism'', () pp. 91–3, UNC Press, ISBN 978-0-8078-4674-2</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Singer|first1=Margaret|authorlink1=Margaret_Singer|last2=Lalich|first2=Janja|authorlink2=Janja_Lalich|title=Cults in Our Midst|isbn=0-7879-0266-7|oclc=35979557|quote=... only 5 to 6 percent of cult members demonstrate major psychological problems prior to joining ...|date=September 1996}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Tourish|first=Dennis|date=16 July 2005|title=How cults can produce killers|journal=The Irish Times|location=[[Dublin|Dublin]]|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/opinion/2005/0716/1121383465767.html|accessdate=1 September 2010|quote=... researchers have found no correlation between cult membership and psychological disorder. Counterintuitively, most cult members are of at least average intelligence and have perfectly normal personality profiles. ...|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111119093555/http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/opinion/2005/0716/1121383465767.html|archive-date=2011-11-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>美国{{link-en|宗教科学研究协会|Society for the Scientific Study of Religion}}<ref>''Society for the Scientific Study of Religion'', council meeting on 7 November 1990 [http://rra.hartsem.edu/sssr/SSSR/BUSINESS/90.html (Online)] {{Wayback|url=http://rra.hartsem.edu/sssr/SSSR/BUSINESS/90.html |date=20110102125002 }}</ref>在1990年指出，没有足够的研究就此事達成共識，而且「不應該自動将人身強制和控制的技术等同于非物质性的強制和控制的技术」，甚至目前學界已拋棄邪教搞洗腦的假說，<ref name="Elizabeth Aileen Young">{{cite journal |author1=Elizabeth Aileen Young |title=The use of the »Brainwashing« Theory by the Anti-cult Movement in the United States of America, pre-1996 |journal=Zeitschrift für junge Religionswissenschaft |date=2012-07 |volume=7 |pages=5-19 |doi=https://doi.org/10.4000/zjr.387}}</ref><ref name = "Dick Anthony and Thomas Robbins">{{cite journal |author1=Dick Anthony and Thomas Robbins |title=Conversion and "Brainwashing" in New Religious Movements |journal=Centre for Studies on New Religions |date=2004 |pages=1-40 |url=https://www.cesnur.org/2003/brain_conv.htm |accessdate=2021-04-03 |archive-date=2021-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423075316/https://www.cesnur.org/2003/brain_conv.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，现在大多數社會科學家認為在對宗教運動的研究中，一些人所提出的精神控制的理論并沒有获得科學印证，就連「[[邪教|邪教]]」本身，也開始被學者認為是一個無效的概念，換句話說，沒有「某某信仰是邪教」這回事；此外，在美國，由於[[美國憲法第一修正案|美國憲法第一修正案]]之故，因此政府極少干涉宗教自由，而多數被視為非法的宗教團體都涉及對他人的犯罪活動；而在美國憲法第一修正案的保護下，諸如「[[洗腦|洗腦]]」、強力說服信徒捐獻、非常規醫療措施等各種看似「邪門」的作為，在事實上都是受保障的，甚至「洗腦」的說法本身，也被認為是一個具有強烈主觀性的用語。<ref name="HG">{{cite web |title=Are Cults Legal? |url=https://www.hg.org/legal-articles/are-cults-legal-35055 |website=HG.org Legal Resources |access-date=2021-07-26 |archive-date=2021-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210724165305/https://www.hg.org/legal-articles/are-cults-legal-35055 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

